      "orig": "We obtain the transpose of a matrix by exchanging its rows and columns.  In other words, the entry in row i column j of A is the entry in row j column i of A T .",
      "text": "We obtain the transpose of a matrix by exchanging its rows and columns.  In other words, the entry in row i column j of A is the entry in row j column i of A T ."
